ENGLISH:
Sharkhunter Updates (Version V1.2.1):
- Amiibo functionality (Codes), uses the Amiibo base as a reference (ONLY WORKS WITH BOWSER, for now...).
- Map set in Bowser's volcanic castle.
- Bowser's exclusive mode, SHOWTIME.
Version V1.2.2
- Fixed the enable flags button bug, it now displays when it's active and when it's not.
- Fixed SHOWTIME mode, which is now more difficult... AND MORE FUN.
